descriptor.name: Pure Shilajit Resin Form With Ashwagandha 20 g
descriptor.code: Pure Shilajit Resin Form With Ashwagandha 20 g
descriptor.short_desc: UPAKARMA Pure Shilajit Resin with Ashwagandha 20g | Boost Strength & Build Muscle Mass Naturally | 100% Ayurvedic
descriptor.long_desc:
Enhances Physical Strength - Shilajit with Ashwagandha helps in boosting strength by providing essential nutrients and promoting muscle growth, enabling the body to perform better to attain your physical goals. This powerful combination revitalizes the body, and helps in enhancing stamina and endurance
 Builds Muscle Mass - Shilajit contains more than 80 essential minerals that help in energy production and muscle recovery, while Ashwagandha helps in enhancing muscle growth & strength
 Improves Vigor & Vitality - Shilajit helps in enhancing nutrient absorption, detoxifying the body, and strengthening overall physical well-being, while Ashwagandha helps in reducing anxiety and maintaining hormonal balance. Together, they promote vigor, stamina, and overall well-being
 Boosts Immunity - Shilajit is well-known for boosting the immune system. It contains a potent blend of minerals that helps in enhancing the body's natural defense system, while Ashwagandha revitalizes the body and promotes mental calmness. Together, they increase energy levels and strengthen overall immunity
 Reduces Stress & Anxiety - Shilajit supports the nervous system, while Ashwagandha promotes relaxation by regulating cortisol levels. Together, they provide adaptogenic properties that help in managing stress and promoting overall well-being
 Improves Sleeping Pattern - Shilajit is rich in minerals and fulvic acid, which helps in enhancing overall health and vitality. Ashwagandha is an adaptogenic herb that helps in reducing stress & promoting a sense of calmness. Together they help in promoting sound sleep
 Assured Quality - With Upakarma, you get the best quality in the segment as all our products are 100% natural and go through 7+ levels of quality checks, which are also AYUSH approved and GMP Certified
 How To Use - Take a pea-sized amount of Upakarma Shilajit Resin with Ashwagandha and dissolve it in 100 - 200 ml of lukewarm milk or water. Stir it thoroughly and drink. For best results, it is advisable to consume twice a day or as directed by the physician

descriptor.name: Pure Shilajit Resin Form With Gold Dust 20 g
descriptor.code: Pure Shilajit Resin Form With Gold Dust 20 g
descriptor.short_desc: UPAKARMA Ayurveda | Premium Shilajit Gold Dust Resin 20g | 100% Ayurvedic | Pure and Natural Shilajeet | Helps to Boost Immunity, Energy, Strength, Stamina, and Overall Health
descriptor.long_desc:
PURE SHILAJIT - Pure Shilajit Gold Dust by Upakarma Ayurveda is a powerful health and immunity booster. The high concentration of minerals, Fulvic, and Humic acids in Shilajit provides innumerable benefits. It is a natural dietary supplement with Gold Vark, having a positive impact on physical and mental well-being.
 MORE POWER AND STRENGTH - The Main benefit of Shilajit is helps to improve energy levels which significantly improves strength and stamina. Fulvic acid and Humic acid present in Shilajit help attain more power for better athletic performance.
 GOLD BENEFITS - Swarna Vang is an ancient ayurvedic medicine that has numerous health benefits such as helping better cell regeneration and cell recovery which leads to faster healing. In addition, Shilajit Gold Dust contains anti-ageing properties that help boost collagen production leads to better skin elasticity, thus promotes healthy, youthful, and glowing skin.
 NO ADDED CHEMICALS - Premium Quality Shilajit Gold Dust 20 grams by Upakarma Ayurveda is free from any chemicals, binders, or filler and is only made from pure and natural ingredients.
 HOW TO USE FOR BEST RESULTS - Take a pea-sized amount of Upakarma Ayurveda Pure Shilajit Resin with Gold Dust and dissolve it in 100 - 200 ml of lukewarm milk or water. Stir it thoroughly and drink. For best results, it is advisable to consume twice a day.
 NATURAL AND LAB-TESTED FOR QUALITY - We don’t believe in compromising on the quality; moreover all our products are manufactured under GMP & ISO certified units.
